00:02:51.349 --> 00:02:55.510
This particular schema is used to keep the
number line relatively centered over multiple

00:02:55.510 --> 00:02:56.510
print runs.

00:02:56.510 --> 00:03:01.270
Further demonstrating the lack of standardization
across publishers for the printer's key, the

00:03:01.270 --> 00:03:05.370
